// 01_hello_world.bund
// The simplest possible BUND program: push a string, print it.

"Hello, world!" println

// Multiple lines of output
"BUND is stack-based." println
"Values are pushed left to right." println
"Commands consume values from the top of the stack." println

// Numbers are also values; println converts them to text
42 println
3.14159 println
true println
